org.xmappr
Class XMLSimpleReader

java.lang.Object
  org.xmappr.XMLSimpleReader

public class XMLSimpleReader
extends java.lang.Object

A wrapper around XMLStreamReader that enables access to XML on the element level. It's no longer necessary to create a loop pulling and processing events. A simple usage example:

XMLSimpleReader reader = new XMLSimpleReader(xmlStreamReader);
reader.getNodeName();
reader.getAttributes();

Author:
peter
